	<body>
		<h1>Make up a User ID</h1>
		[ <a href="login">Login</a> - <a href="do-logout">Logout</a> ]
		<p>Please enter a  username - anything will do, it's just needed to test the handling of the recordContentSource field. (In our application the recordContentSource field will be populated with the user id of the person who last edited the record).</p>
		<form action="do-login" method="post">
			<p>Username: <input type="text" name="username"/>
			</p>
			<p>
				<input type="submit"/>
			</p>
		</form>
	</body>
